    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.2)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 0.9.0),
    knitr,
    ape
SystemRequirements: C++11
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LinkingTo: Rcpp
